<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Garuda Bitcoin Blueprint | Strategic Digital Treasury Reserve</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fontsource/inter@5.0.19/index.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --merah: #E11A2B;
            --putih: #FFFFFF;
            --emas: #D4AF37;
            --gelap: #0B0F19;
            --gelap-light: #151B2B;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--gelap);
            color: var(--putih);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .text-merah { color: var(--merah); }
        .bg-merah { background-color: var(--merah); }
        .text-emas { color: var(--emas); }
        .border-emas { border-color: var(--emas); }
        .bg-emas { background-color: var(--emas); }
        .glass {
            background: rgba(21, 27, 43, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }
        .glass-strong {
            background: rgba(21, 27, 43, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--putih) 0%, var(--emas) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .hero-bg {
            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.6), rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.95)), url('https://image.qwenlm.ai/public_source/bd6cd4f4-4caf-4474-9fee-47f4242ea23c/1fcc6b171-dfab-4f0f-9fa9-7fff9381c7bf.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .animate-fade-up {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        .animate-fade-up.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .flywheel-ring {
            animation: spin-slow 20s linear infinite;
        }
        .flywheel-ring-reverse {
            animation: spin-slow-reverse 25s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin-slow {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        @keyframes spin-slow-reverse {
            from { transform: rotate(360deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        }
        .timeline-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--merah), var(--emas), var(--gelap));
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .timeline-line { left: 20px; }
        }
        .tab-active {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--emas);
            color: var(--emas);
        }
        .pulse-gold {
            animation: pulse-gold 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse-gold {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 glass border-b border-white/5 transition-all duration-300" id="navbar">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-merah flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white text-xs">GB</div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-lg tracking-wide">GARUDA BITCOIN</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">
                    <a href="#strategi" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Strategi Makro</a>
                    <a href="#korporasi" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Treasury Korporasi</a>
                    <a href="#regulasi" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Evolusi Regulasi</a>
                    <a href="#roadmap" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Roadmap 10 Tahun</a>
                    <a href="#kontak" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Kontak</a>
                </div>
                <button class="md:hidden text-white focus:outline-none" id="mobile-menu-btn">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:hidden hidden bg-gelap-light border-t border-white/10" id="mobile-menu">
            <div class="px-4 py-3 space-y-2">
                <a href="#strategi" class="block py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Strategi Makro</a>
                <a href="#korporasi" class="block py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Treasury Korporasi</a>
                <a href="#regulasi" class="block py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Evolusi Regulasi</a>
                <a href="#roadmap" class="block py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Roadmap</a>
                <a href="#kontak" class="block py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Kontak</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative pt-16">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center animate-fade-up">
            <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider text-emas border border-emas/30 rounded-full bg-emas/10">
                BLUEPRINT 2026
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
                <span class="text-merah">MER</span> <span class="text-white">AH PUT</span> <span class="text-merah">IH</span><br>
                <span class="gradient-text">Strategic Digital Treasury</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Transisi Indonesia menuju ketahanan finansial berbasis hard asset digital. 
                Bitcoin sebagai cadangan nilai nasional, lindung nilai korporasi, dan katalis energi terbarukan.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#strategi" class="px-8 py-3 bg-merah hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-red-900/30">
                    Pelajari Blueprint
                </a>
                <a href="#flywheel" class="px-8 py-3 border border-white/20 hover:border-emas hover:text-emas text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all glass">
                    Efek Roda Gila Garuda
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"/></svg>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Strategic Pillars -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gelap" id="pilar">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Tiga Pilar Strategis</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Bukan koin baru atau pengganti Rupiah. Ini adalah narasi strategis kedaulatan finansial Indonesia.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Sovereign -->
                <div class="glass-strong p-8 rounded-2xl hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-up">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-merah">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 21v-8a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8M3 21h18M5 21v-6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v6m-14 0H5"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Sovereign Reserve Asset</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Menyimpan Bitcoin sebagai cadangan nilai nasional ("emas digital") bersama USD dan emas fisik. Sovereign Bitcoin Fund (SBF) dikelola BI & Kemenkeu.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-emas">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emas rounded-full mr-2"></span> Alokasi 1%-5% Cadangan Devisa
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Corporate -->
                <div class="glass-strong p-8 rounded-2xl hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-400">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Corporate Treasury</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Institusi dan perusahaan mengalokasikan kas dalam Bitcoin sebagai lindung nilai (hedge) terhadap inflasi dan devaluasi Rupiah struktural.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-blue-400">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span> Proteksi Neraca & Kolateral
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Education -->
                <div class="glass-strong p-8 rounded-2xl hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-400">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">National Education</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Kampanye kesadaran finansial anti-devaluasi untuk publik dan pembuat kebijakan. Literasi hard asset untuk generasi 2045.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-green-400">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span> Data Empiris & Kesadaran Publik
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Macro Strategy -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gelap-light relative overflow-hidden" id="strategi">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-merah/10 rounded-full filter blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="animate-fade-up">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Strategi Makro: <span class="text-emas">Sovereign Bitcoin Fund</span></h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-merah">1</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Backstop Currency Rupiah</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Bitcoin sebagai penopang stabilisasi nilai tukar saat krisis global. Alokasi bertahap 1%-5% dari cadangan devisa.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-merah">2</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Hedging Ekspor Komoditas</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Mengubah surplus komoditas (minyak, sawit, nikel) menjadi hard asset digital tanpa konversi ke fiat asing.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 text-xs font-bold text-merah">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Energy Arbitrage & Monetisasi</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Memanfaatkan energi geothermal, hydro, dan gas flare untuk mining. Input Layer → Processing Layer → Output Layer (Akumulasi Nasional).</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl animate-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">Alur Monetisasi Energi</span>
                        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-emas/10 text-emas rounded">Zero-Devisa</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gelap/50 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-green-900/30 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-green-400 text-xs">⚡</div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Input Layer</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Geothermal, Hydro, Gas Flare</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right text-xs text-green-400">Energi Terstranded</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-600">↓</div>
                        <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gelap/50 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-blue-900/30 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-blue-400 text-xs">🏭</div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Processing Layer</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Infrastruktur Komputasi (Mining)</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right text-xs text-blue-400">Hash Power</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-center text-gray-600">↓</div>
                        <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gelap/50 rounded-lg border border-emas/20">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-yellow-900/30 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-yellow-400 text-xs">₿</div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Output Layer</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Akumulasi Bitcoin Nasional</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-right text-xs text-emas pulse-gold rounded px-2">Reserve Asset</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Corporate Treasury Matrix -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gelap" id="korporasi">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Matriks Alokasi Corporate Treasury</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Proteksi kas, optimalisasi neraca, dan kolateral berdaulat untuk pertumbuhan jangka panjang.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-strong rounded-2xl p-1 animate-fade-up">
                <div class="flex border-b border-white/10 mb-4 px-4">
                    <button class="py-3 px-4 text-sm font-medium tab-active transition-colors" onclick="switchTab(event, 'konservatif')">Konservatif</button>
                    <button class="py-3 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" onclick="switchTab(event, 'berimbang')">Berimbang</button>
                    <button class="py-3 px-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" onclick="switchTab(event, 'agresif')">Agresif</button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-4 md:p-8">
                    <!-- Konservatif -->
                    <div id="tab-konservatif" class="tab-content block">
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Profil Konservatif</h3>
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emas mb-4">1 - 3% <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">dari Kas</span></div>
                                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Tujuan: Cash protection awal, pengenalan sistem arsitektur kustodian. Cocok untuk perusahaan yang baru memulai eksplorasi aset digital.</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Pemahaman dewan direksi & audit infrastruktur</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Cold Storage Multi-signature</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> DCA (Dollar-Cost Averaging) rutin</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gelap/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Alokasi Bitcoin</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
                                    <div class="bg-gray-500 h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 15%"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between mt-4 mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Cadangan Kas</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
                                    <div class="bg-white/80 h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 85%"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Berimbang -->
                    <div id="tab-berimbang" class="tab-content hidden">
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Profil Berimbang</h3>
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emas mb-4">5 - 10% <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">dari Kas</span></div>
                                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Tujuan: Lindung nilai inflasi struktural, balance sheet optimization. Menerapkan standar akuntansi IFRS dan SOP manajemen risiko.</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Integrasi standar akuntansi (IFRS)</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Tata kelola (governance) ketat berskala audit</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Horizon investasi jangka panjang (5+ tahun)</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gelap/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Alokasi Bitcoin</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
                                    <div class="bg-emas h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 35%"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between mt-4 mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Cadangan Kas</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
                                    <div class="bg-white/80 h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 65%"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Agresif -->
                    <div id="tab-agresif" class="tab-content hidden">
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Profil Agresif</h3>
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emas mb-4">10 - 20% <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-normal">dari Kas</span></div>
                                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Tujuan: Long-term value storage, eksposur maksimal terhadap hard asset. Bitcoin aktif digunakan sebagai pelindung neraca dan kolateral keuangan.</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Strategic asset treasury integration</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Kolateral untuk future lending korporasi</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Benchmark: MicroStrategy, Metaplanet</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gelap/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex justify-between mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Alokasi Bitcoin</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
                                    <div class="bg-merah h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 55%"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between mt-4 mb-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Cadangan Kas</div>
                                <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-4">
